## 6️⃣ 상태 머신 설계 (State Machine)

### 6.1 상태와 전이(Transition)

```rust
#[derive(Debug)]
enum State {
    IDLE,
    RUNNING(u32),    // 코어ID
    ERROR(String),   // 에러 메시지
}

let current_state = State::RUNNING(7);

match current_state {
    State::IDLE => {
        println!("대기 중... 작업 대기");
    }
    State::RUNNING(core_id) => {
        println!("코어 {} 실행 중", core_id);
    }
    State::ERROR(msg) => {
        println!("오류 발생: {}", msg);
    }
}
```

### 6.2 상태 전이 로직

```rust
enum Event {
    Start,
    Load(u32),     // 부하 레벨
    Shutdown,
}

let next_state = match (current_state, event) {
    (State::IDLE, Event::Start) => State::RUNNING(1),
    (State::RUNNING(id), Event::Load(level)) if level > 80 => {
        State::ERROR("Overload".to_string())
    }
    (State::RUNNING(id), Event::Load(_)) => State::RUNNING(id),
    (State::RUNNING(_), Event::Shutdown) => State::IDLE,
    (State::ERROR(_), Event::Start) => State::RUNNING(1),
    (state, _) => state,  // 다른 모든 경우
};
```

